{"id":57267,"date":"2024-06-24T12:15:00","date_gmt":"2024-06-24T06:45:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=57267"},"modified":"2024-06-27T14:17:49","modified_gmt":"2024-06-27T08:47:49","slug":"10-modern-small-kitchen-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/10-modern-small-kitchen-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"10 Modern Small Kitchen Ideas to Maximise Space in Compact Homes"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>10 modern small kitchen ideas to enhance your culinary space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To keep up with the demand for convenient living spaces, homes are shrinking. A small kitchen can feel like a culinary challenge where living spaces are often at a premium. But who says small kitchens can&#8217;t pack a big punch in both style and functionality?&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Whether you are a budding chef or a takeout aficionado, a <strong>modern minimalist <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/types-of-small-kitchen-designs\/\"><strong>small kitchen<\/strong><\/a> can be the heart of your home with the right design ideas. Here are ten smart and chic solutions to transform your compact kitchen into a practical and Pinterest-worthy space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Look Neat With Open Shelving in a Modern Small Kitchen Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Open shelving can make a small kitchen feel larger and more open. Replacing traditional cabinets with open shelves creates a sense of depth and gives easy access to everyday items. Plus, it&#8217;s a great way to display your beautiful dishware and glassware. This <strong>modern, small, <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/open-kitchen-design\/\"><strong>open kitchen design idea<\/strong><\/a><strong> <\/strong>uses uniform containers for storage to keep the shelves looking neat. Limiting the number of items on each shelf helps to avoid clutter.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105054\/modern-small-kitchen-with-open-shelving.jpg\" alt=\"Modern small kitchen ideas with open shelving to add depth\" class=\"wp-image-57269\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105054\/modern-small-kitchen-with-open-shelving.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105054\/modern-small-kitchen-with-open-shelving-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105054\/modern-small-kitchen-with-open-shelving-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105054\/modern-small-kitchen-with-open-shelving-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105054\/modern-small-kitchen-with-open-shelving-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Add depth and accessibility through open shelves<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Multi-Functional Furniture for Small Space Modern Kitchen Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Every piece of furniture should serve multiple purposes in a small kitchen. Consider an island that can double as a dining table or a prep station that can be tucked away when not in use. A <strong>small modern <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/types-of-kitchen-tables\/\"><strong>kitchen table<\/strong><\/a><strong> and chairs<\/strong> should be crafted keeping the limited space in mind. Take, for instance, a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/dining-room-interiors\/foldable-dining-table\/\">foldable dining table<\/a> that can be extended when needed or stools that can be stored under the counter to save space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105104\/modern-small-kitchen-with-multi-functional-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"Modern small kitchen ideas with multi-functional furniture to maximise utility\" class=\"wp-image-57270\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105104\/modern-small-kitchen-with-multi-functional-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105104\/modern-small-kitchen-with-multi-functional-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105104\/modern-small-kitchen-with-multi-functional-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105104\/modern-small-kitchen-with-multi-functional-furniture-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105104\/modern-small-kitchen-with-multi-functional-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Multi-functional furniture maximises utility<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Bright &amp; Light Colours in Small House Modern Kitchen Tiles Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Light colours can make a small space feel bigger and more inviting. Opt for whites, light greys, or soft pastels for your kitchen walls, cabinets, and counters, making <strong>small house <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/modern-kitchen-design\/\"><strong>modern kitchen design<\/strong><\/a> look fuller. Reflective surfaces like glossy tiles or glass can also enhance the sense of space. White subway tiles for the backsplash or a bright yellow backsplash with overall white are good ideas for space optimisation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105123\/modern-small-kitchen-tiles-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Modern small kitchen tiles ideas in bright and light colours\" class=\"wp-image-57272\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105123\/modern-small-kitchen-tiles-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105123\/modern-small-kitchen-tiles-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105123\/modern-small-kitchen-tiles-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105123\/modern-small-kitchen-tiles-ideas-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105123\/modern-small-kitchen-tiles-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Go bright and light in tile selection in compact kitchens<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Smart Storage Solutions in Modern Small U-shaped Kitchen Designs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Maximise your storage with <strong>modern small kitchen design ideas<\/strong> using smart solutions such as pull-out drawers, Lazy Susans, and vertical storage racks. These can help you make the most of every inch of your kitchen. Integrating pull-out pantry shelves for easy access to ingredients or magnetic knife strips to save counter space are intelligent ways of improving your kitchen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105133\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Modern small u-shaped kitchen ideas with smart storage solutions\" class=\"wp-image-57273\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105133\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105133\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105133\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105133\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-storage-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105133\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Smart storage solutions are a must for an efficient home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Compact Appliances in a Modern Small Modular Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best <strong>modern small white kitchen ideas<\/strong> is a space inclusive of modern compact appliances designed to fit smaller spaces without sacrificing functionality. Look for slimline refrigerators, dishwashers, and integrated ovens that can handle your cooking needs without taking up too much space. A two-burner stovetop instead of a full-sized range or a combination of microwave and convection oven can do wonders.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105031\/modern-small-kitchen-with-compact-appliances.jpg\" alt=\"Modern small kitchen ideas with compact appliances designed to fit smaller spaces\" class=\"wp-image-57268\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105031\/modern-small-kitchen-with-compact-appliances.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105031\/modern-small-kitchen-with-compact-appliances-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105031\/modern-small-kitchen-with-compact-appliances-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105031\/modern-small-kitchen-with-compact-appliances-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105031\/modern-small-kitchen-with-compact-appliances-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"> Compact homes need compact appliances <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Multi functional kitchen spaces for compact homes\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/06165221\/multi-functional-kitchen-spaces-for-compact-homes-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Integrated Lighting in a Modern Small Open Kitchen Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Good lighting is essential in a <strong>modern small modular kitchen<\/strong>. Use a mix of task, ambient, and accent lighting to create a cosy, well-lit space. For task lighting, you can go for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/choosing-kitchen-under-cabinet-lighting\/\">under-cabinet LED lights<\/a> or pendant lights above the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/everything-know-about-kitchen-islands\/\">kitchen island<\/a> or dining area. Good lighting can brighten up the space and make your kitchen come alive without spending big bucks.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105141\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-lighting.jpg\" alt=\"Modern small open kitchen ideas with integrated lighting to enhance the interior\" class=\"wp-image-57274\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105141\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-lighting.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105141\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-lighting-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105141\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-lighting-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105141\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-lighting-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105141\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-lighting-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Integrated lighting enhances every style of kitchen interior<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. Modern Minimalist Small Kitchen Design Goals<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Modern small kitchen ideas<\/strong> are incomplete without exploring a minimalist design to keep your culinary space from feeling overcrowded. Focus on clean lines, simple designs, and functional pieces. Avoid unnecessary decor and keep surfaces clear. Choose sleek, handleless cabinets and keep the colour palette simple and cohesive.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105210\/minimalist-modern-small-kitchen-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Modern small kitchen ideas which is minimalist and keep the kitchen uncluttered\" class=\"wp-image-57277\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105210\/minimalist-modern-small-kitchen-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105210\/minimalist-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105210\/minimalist-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105210\/minimalist-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105210\/minimalist-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"> Minimalist design keeps the kitchen uncluttered<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">8. Tiled Backsplash for a Small House Modern Kitchen Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A white tiled backsplash can reflect light and create the illusion of a larger space. It is a stylish and modern choice that can make your kitchen look airy. With a contrasting and vibrant wall colour like red, it can work like magic for your space. A tiled backsplash enhances natural light while adding a perfect touch of elegance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105151\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-backsplash.jpg\" alt=\"Modern small kitchen ideas with a tiled backsplash in red and white colour\" class=\"wp-image-57275\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105151\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-backsplash.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105151\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-backsplash-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105151\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-backsplash-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105151\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-backsplash-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105151\/modern-small-kitchen-ideas-with-backsplash-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A red and white kitchen with hints of black<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">9. Create a Mini Kitchen Garden in a Small Mid-Century Modern Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bring a touch of greenery into your small kitchen with a random arrangement of indoor plants. This can be a space-saving way to grow herbs and small plants, adding freshness and a pop of colour to your overall kitchen look. Wondering where to start? Install a vertical planter or a rack on an empty wall. Use small pots or hanging planters for herbs and succulents to give a clean look.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105218\/mid-century-modern-small-kitchen-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Modern small kitchen ideas in mid-century style with a small garden\" class=\"wp-image-57278\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105218\/mid-century-modern-small-kitchen-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105218\/mid-century-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105218\/mid-century-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105218\/mid-century-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105218\/mid-century-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"> Vertical gardening adds freshness to this modern kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">10. Customise Your Modern Small L-Shaped Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sometimes, the best solutions are those tailored specifically for your space. Consider custom-built cabinets, drawers, and islands that fit your kitchen&#8217;s unique dimensions and needs. Maximise every inch of space while providing a personalised touch.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105223\/customised-modern-small-kitchen-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Modern small kitchen ideas which are customised solutions for a personal touch\" class=\"wp-image-57279\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105223\/customised-modern-small-kitchen-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105223\/customised-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105223\/customised-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105223\/customised-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/26105223\/customised-modern-small-kitchen-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"> Customised solutions personalise the space\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Even the smallest kitchen can become a stylish and useful area with the help of these 10 <strong>modern small kitchen ideas<\/strong>. From optimising storage with clever solutions to creating an open, airy vibe with bright colours and open shelving, your kitchen can become a centre of efficiency and elegance. Remember that every component should improve your kitchen&#8217;s overall appearance and usability by carefully balancing design and functionality. Put these contemporary compact kitchen design concepts into practice now. Start implementing these modern small kitchen design ideas with our expert design consultants, waiting right here to help you out:<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\"> Contact Us | Home Interior Design | DesignCafe<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Modern Small Kitchen Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How do you design a small modern kitchen?<\/strong><br>Designing a small modern kitchen involves maximising space with smart storage solutions, using multi-functional furniture, incorporating compact appliances, and choosing a minimalist design with clean lines. Embrace open shelving to create depth, and consider custom-built cabinets to fit your kitchen&#8217;s unique dimensions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How do you brighten a small, dull kitchen?<\/strong><br>Brighten a small, dull kitchen by using light colours like whites and pastels on walls and cabinets. Incorporate reflective surfaces like glossy tiles or a mirrored backsplash. Add ample lighting, including under-cabinet LED and pendant lights, to create a well-lit, inviting space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What colours are best for a small modern kitchen?<\/strong><br>The best colours for a small modern kitchen are light and neutral shades, such as white, light grey, and soft pastels. These colours make the space feel larger and more open. Adding pops of colour through accessories or a statement backsplash can provide visual interest without overwhelming the space.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example dro